Setup:

1. npm create vite@latest

2. Install shadcn

3. Setup supabase and create tables in supabase

4. install react-router-dom

5. Create all the pages and components

6. Add shadcn components and images/button/forms

7. Do the form actions (Buttons, onSubmit, routing)

8. Auth-> write logic for signup or login to show

9. auth API setup

10. login & signup component + state management + Yup (Validation)

11. useFetch -> handling API calls (Login)

12. If login credentials is valid then navigate to that search param

13. Setup signup page, use context.jsx -> to see if user is logged in, then route to /dashboard if signup successful

14. logged in -> navigate '/auth' to '/dashboard' and show user details if logged in and login button otherwise

15. setup and update

